# Copy to apps/mobile/.env.local and set to your Mac's LAN IP, e.g.
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.42:4000
#
# Find your IP: System Settings → Network → Wi-Fi → Details → IP Address.
# The phone must be on the same Wi-Fi as the Mac running `bun run dev:api`.
#
# Alternative (recommended for travel): install Tailscale on Mac and
# iPhone, then use the Tailscale IP here so the app works off-LAN.
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=
